hw2: Drawing Scene in 3D

Santhanakrishnan Ramani
CSCI 4229/5229 Summer 2016
Time Taken = approx 10 hrs

Key bindings
  
  m          Toggle between perspective and orthogonal
  f          Toggle fpn
  w/s        To move forward and backward in fpn mode
  =/-        Changes field of view for perspective
  a          Toggle axes  
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit
  
